g.text: Rounding simplifies a number to a nearby value with fewer digits.

ul.li: If the digit to the right is < 5: Round down.
If the digit to the right is ≥ 5: Round up.

div.p: Example 1: Round 67 to the nearest ten
Example 2: Round 2043 to the nearest thousand
Example 3: Round 914,307 to the nearest ten thousand
